locality: Município de Resende. Mt. Itatiaia, planalto. Base of rock outcrop, Pedra Assentada on west side. The planalto is a steep hilly terrain, many hills toped with ountainous outcrops of bare sienite quartz. Hillsides with frequent rounded outcropping quartz rocks & boulders, and a thin, black almost pur humus soil supporting a periodically-burned, natural tussock sedge-grassland (mainly Cladium) with scattered low chusquea bamboo & occasionally othe shrubs.
